source: TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_YOJINBO_000_000<tab>For far, far too long have I waited for this rematch!
target: TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_YOJINBO_000_000<tab>For far, far too long have I waited for this rematch!

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_YOJINBO_100_000The Soboro Sukehiro may have brought us together, but 'twas fate that
ordained we engage in glorious fisticuffs─but with swords!─once more!
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_YOJINBO_100_000The Soboro Sukehiro may have brought us together, but 'twas fate that
ordained we engage in glorious fisticuffs─but with swords!─once more!

source: TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_GILGAMESH_000_011<tab>I throw myself upon your boundless mercy and beg forgiveness! Please!
target: TEXT_DUNGEONFESYOJINBO_00000_GILGAMESH_000_011<tab>I throw myself upon your boundless mercy and beg forgiveness! Please!
